snippet.title: Zero Caliber 2 - Official Release Date Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: From icy environments to countryside settings and more, check out action-packed gameplay from Zero Caliber 2 in this latest trailer for the upcoming VR FPS game sequel. Zero Caliber 2 will be available on Meta Quest on July 11, 2024.
